data.displayName: SA _ ENGIE Home Business GreenPower Gas

fees.description: A $2.20 (inc. GST) charge will apply to paper bills sent in the post.
You may be charged a 0.32% merchant service fee for paying by Visa or Mastercard (unless you pay via direct debit).
A fee of $12 may apply for payments made after the due date (GST exempt).

gasContract.terms: For further details on the information presented in this Plan Information Document, or for full terms and conditions, please visit www.engie.com.au or call ENGIE on 13 88 08

discounts.description: You'll receive a 10% guaranteed discount off our gas usage and supply charges.

gasContract.variation: We may vary your rates and charges at any time, including if any underlying information is incorrect, you get a new meter or your distributor changes your tariff. We'll give you advance notice of any change, which may be on your bill.

eligibility.description: Offer only available to Home Business customers.

gasContract.onExpiryDescription: Ongoing energy plan until you or we end it. We may end this energy plan at any time by giving you 20 Business Days' notice.
gasContract.additionalFeeInformation: Additional fees may apply. For information please contact us on 13 88 08.
